~ start
do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_activated.emit()
Nathan: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], this is TEST dialogue.
Nathan: Here are some choices.
- First one
	Nathan: You picked the first one. 
- Second one
	Nathan: You picked the second one.
- Start again => start
- End the conversation 
	do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_deactivated.emit() 
	=> END
	
Nathan: For more information see the online documentation.

=> END

~ start_npc_gabbi
do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_activated.emit()
Gabbi: Hi, would you like to help me?
- Yes
	Gabbi: You got a job for me?
	- Yes
		Gabbi: Cool, ill take that
	- No
		do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_deactivated.emit() 
		=> END
- No
	Gabbi: Too bad...
	do BaseDialougeManager.dialouge_deactivated.emit() 
	=> END